<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:08:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄罗斯法院判处资深活动家奥尔洛夫 2.5 年监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-court-jails-veteran-activist-orlov-for-2-5-years/articleshow/108045617.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108045617.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯一家法院周二判处高级人权活动家奥列格·奥尔洛夫两年半监禁，罪名是谴责俄罗斯对乌克兰的袭击。法官说：“法院已判定奥尔洛夫有罪，并下令在总政权流放地判处两年零六个月的刑期。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 12:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-court-jails-veteran-activist-orlov-for-2-5-years/articleshow/108045617.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度 bizman 捐赠 2.25 卢比用于释放 900 名囚犯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/as-pre-ramzan-gesture-indian-businessman-donates-rs-2-25-crore-for-release-of-900-prisoners/articleshow/108044460.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108044460.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总部位于迪拜的印度商人 Firoz Merchant of Pure Gold 捐赠 22.5 亿卢比，用于释放阿拉伯国家迪拜海湾监狱中的 900 名囚犯。由麦钱特发起的“被遗忘的社会”倡议已确保 20,000 名囚犯获释。穆罕默德·优素福·马特罗希上校赞扬了麦钱特的努力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:35:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/as-pre-ramzan-gesture-indian-businessman-donates-rs-2-25-crore-for-release-of-900-prisoners/articleshow/108044460.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本提议立法将更多信息列为机密</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-proposes-law-to-classify-more-information-as-confidential/articleshow/108043867.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108043867.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本政府已提议立法扩大机密信息的分类范围，并要求对有权访问该信息的公司员工进行安全检查。然而，反对派议员担心这些新规则可能会侵犯公民自由。日本首相岸田文雄政府认为，日本与西方政府结盟将有助于与国内企业和国际盟友更好地共享信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-proposes-law-to-classify-more-information-as-confidential/articleshow/108043867.cms</guid></item><item><title>纳瓦尔尼盟友敦促俄罗斯人参加选举日抗议活动以纪念他，这引起了克里姆林宫的愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/navalny-ally-urges-russians-to-join-election-day-protest-in-his-memory-drawing-kremlin-ire/articleshow/108042638.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108042638.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;已故反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的亲密盟友敦促俄罗斯人按照纳瓦尔尼生前的呼吁参加下个月针对总统弗拉基米尔·普京的抗议活动。克里姆林宫警告称，那些支持这一“挑衅性呼吁”的人将面临法律后果，克里姆林宫指责这些人是美国支持的危险极端分子。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:34:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/navalny-ally-urges-russians-to-join-election-day-protest-in-his-memory-drawing-kremlin-ire/articleshow/108042638.cms</guid></item><item><title>米尼塔·桑格维 (Minita Sanghvi) 获得民主党正式提名，她可能成为纽约州参议院第一位同性恋女性</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/minita-sanghvi-who-could-be-first-gay-woman-in-ny-senate-gets-official-democratic-nomination/articleshow/108042188.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108042188.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度裔美国人米尼塔·桑格维 (Minita Sanghvi) 获得纽约州第 44 州参议院选区的民主党提名。她得到了萨拉托加县民主委员会和斯克内克塔迪县民主委员会的支持。桑维是斯基德莫尔学院的营销学教授，此前曾在沃尔玛工作。她得到了“印第安人影响力”组织的支持，并将成为纽约参议院第一位公开同性恋身份的女性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/minita-sanghvi-who-could-be-first-gay-woman-in-ny-senate-gets-official-democratic-nomination/articleshow/108042188.cms</guid></item><item><title>几内亚与全国罢工有关的骚乱造成两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-killed-in-guinea-unrest-linked-to-nationwide-strike/articleshow/108041301.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108041301.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，几内亚首都科纳克里郊区发生全国性罢工，导致该市瘫痪并扰乱了一些采矿作业，造成两人死亡。由多个工会组成的伞式组织领导的罢工预计将继续下去。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 09:56:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-killed-in-guinea-unrest-linked-to-nationwide-strike/articleshow/108041301.cms</guid></item><item><title>“在未通知预留席位的情况下不得召开集会”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/no-assembly-session-can-be-called-without-notifying-reserved-seats-says-imran-khans-party/articleshow/108039612.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108039612.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗领导的政党声称，在召集旁遮普省和信德省议会以及首席部长宣誓就职的第二天，在没有首先宣布保留席位的情况下，不得召开省级议会会议。议会应在通知所​​有众议院议员后召开。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 09:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/no-assembly-session-can-be-called-without-notifying-reserved-seats-says-imran-khans-party/articleshow/108039612.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争：普京重组俄罗斯武装部队</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-war-putin-restructures-russian-armed-forces/articleshow/108034496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108034496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 07:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-war-putin-restructures-russian-armed-forces/articleshow/108034496.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京盟友承认俄罗斯对中国的依赖日益加深</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-admits-russias-growing-dependency-on-china/articleshow/108031312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108031312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于乌克兰冲突相关制裁，俄罗斯与西方的关系逐渐疏远，俄罗斯与中国的贸易大幅增加。自2014年吞并克里米亚以来，获得人民币贷款的努力有所加强，但进展仍然有限。尽管寻求中国资本来弥补西方制裁的缺口，但财政部长安东·西卢阿诺夫承认，达成协议仍然遥不可及。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-admits-russias-growing-dependency-on-china/articleshow/108031312.cms</guid></item><item><title>漏油事件给伊拉克农民带来压力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers/articleshow/108030892.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108030892.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊拉克拥有巨大的石油财富，但北部许多贫困的农民表示，原油泄漏污染了他们的土地，给他们已经在与干旱作斗争的压力雪上加霜。伊拉克饱受数十年冲突、腐败和基础设施破败的蹂躏，石油泄漏污染了北部省份的农田，尤其是在冬季降雨期间。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers/articleshow/108030892.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国领导人表示，未来不“排除”西方军队驻扎乌克兰的可能性</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putting-western-troops-on-the-ground-in-ukraine-is-not-ruled-out-in-the-future-french-leader-says/articleshow/108029438.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108029438.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国总统马克龙在欧洲领导人会议后讨论了向乌克兰派遣西方军队的问题。会议未能达成共识，但马克龙强调支持防止俄罗斯侵略。人们仍然对美国的支持和特朗普重返白宫的可能性感到担忧。马克龙拒绝透露哪些国家正在考虑派遣军队的细节，称他更愿意保持一些“战略模糊性”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putting-western-troops-on-the-ground-in-ukraine-is-not-ruled-out-in-the-future-french-leader-says/articleshow/108029438.cms</guid></item><item><title>大多数联合国安理会成员要求塔利班废除严重压迫妇女和女童的法令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/most-un-security-council-members-demand-taliban-rescind-decrees-seriously-oppressing-women-and-girls/articleshow/108028711.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108028711.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国安理会三分之二以上的成员要求塔利班废除所有压迫妇女和女童的政策。理事会谴责塔利班对妇女和女童的镇压，并坚持要求她们平等参与。特使们与塔利班讨论阿富汗路线图，强调包容性、多元化代表性和尊重人权的必要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/most-un-security-council-members-demand-taliban-rescind-decrees-seriously-oppressing-women-and-girls/articleshow/108028711.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在莫斯科：俄罗斯作为中东调解人的角色是什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-in-moscow-what-is-russias-role-as-mideast-mediator/articleshow/108027395.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108027395.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯、法塔赫、巴勒斯坦解放组织等巴勒斯坦各派代表将出席莫斯科会议，就以色列与哈马斯战争、巴勒斯坦权力机构在加沙的作用以及中东问题进行会谈。此次会议旨在展示俄罗斯的影响力并支持巴勒斯坦民族团结。哈马斯自 2007 年以来一直统治加沙，被欧盟、美国和其他国家政府列为恐怖组织。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-in-moscow-what-is-russias-role-as-mideast-mediator/articleshow/108027395.cms</guid></item><item><title>泰勒·斯威夫特的父亲被指控在澳大利亚殴打摄影师</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/taylor-swifts-dad-accused-of-punching-photographer-in-australia/articleshow/108026256.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108026256.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当地新闻来源的报道显示，受害者是一名澳大利亚摄影师，在悉尼港夜间郊游后，她一直在中立湾码头等待泰勒·斯威夫特和她的父亲抵达。但她的父亲已经上了车。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/taylor-swifts-dad-accused-of-punching-photographer-in-australia/articleshow/108026256.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国总统拜登希望加沙在下周一之前实现休战</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-holds-hope-for-gaza-truce-by-next-monday/articleshow/108025647.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108025647.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登希望下周在加沙实现停火。在巴黎会议期间达成了相互谅解。会谈正在穆斯林斋月期间进行。卡塔尔埃米尔和哈马斯领导人讨论立即停火。以色列的军事行动导致加沙地带死亡和人质。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-holds-hope-for-gaza-truce-by-next-monday/articleshow/108025647.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄克拉荷马州 16 岁非二元学生死亡引发美国部分州反跨性别法的关注</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/death-of-non-binary-student-16-in-oklahoma-spotlights-anti-trans-laws-in-some-us-states/articleshow/108025482.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108025482.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄克拉荷马州一所学校卫生间发生争执，一名非二元学生向嘲笑他们的女孩泼水，导致其死亡。该事件引起了广泛关注，凸显了跨性别学生面临的危险以及解决 LGBTQ 学生权利的必要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/death-of-non-binary-student-16-in-oklahoma-spotlights-anti-trans-laws-in-some-us-states/articleshow/108025482.cms</guid></item><item><title>下议院议员指责印度跨国镇压英国锡克教徒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/mp-in-commons-accuses-india-of-transnational-repression-of-uk-sikhs/articleshow/108021972.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108021972.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国议员普利特·吉尔对与印度有关的个人对英国锡克教徒进行跨国镇压表示担忧。吉尔质疑安全部长汤姆·图根哈特为解决这一问题而采取的措施的有效性。五眼国家对与印度有关的个人针对英国锡克教活动人士的攻击表示担忧。吉尔是在下议院内政部口头质询期间发表上述言论的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/mp-in-commons-accuses-india-of-transnational-repression-of-uk-sikhs/articleshow/108021972.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦一名身穿阿拉伯文连衣裙的女子从暴徒手中获救</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/woman-in-arabic-script-dress-saved-from-mob-in-pakistan/articleshow/108022030.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108022030.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周日，在拉合尔繁忙的 Ichra Bazaar，警方迅速介入，从暴徒手中救出了一名身穿阿拉伯书法连衣裙的年轻女孩。暴民指控她亵渎神灵。 300多人将这名女子强行带到附近的一家餐馆，并要求她脱掉衣服，情况变得很糟糕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:50:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/woman-in-arabic-script-dress-saved-from-mob-in-pakistan/articleshow/108022030.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国反腐机构首次调查“一带一路”项目</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-body-to-probe-bri-projects-for-the-first-time/articleshow/108025421.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108025421.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国国家主席习近平的万亿美元贸易和基础设施一带一路倡议将因腐败指控和债务陷阱而受到中央纪律检查委员会的调查。李希领导的中纪委将把体制改革、廉政建设和司法机构建设放在首位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 00:50:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-body-to-probe-bri-projects-for-the-first-time/articleshow/108025421.cms</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利批准后瑞典将成为北约成员国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/sweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid/articleshow/108020284.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108020284.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;匈牙利议会批准了瑞典加入北约的申请，这是瑞典在俄罗斯入侵乌克兰期间加入北约的最后一步。该批准以 188 票赞成、6 票反对的结果标志着一个历史性的时刻，使瑞典成为北约第 32 个成员国。北约秘书长斯托尔滕贝格对这一决定表示欢迎，强调其对加强欧洲-大西洋安全的重要性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 16:30:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/sweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid/articleshow/108020284.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>